      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·魏風·007.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">碩鼠.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>碩鼠碩鼠，無食我黍！三歲貫女，莫我肯顧。逝將去女，適彼樂土。樂土樂土，爰得我所。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Large rats! Large rats!
Do not eat our millet.
Three years have we had to do with you,
And you have not been willing to show any regard for us.
We will leave you,
And go to that happy land.
Happy land! Happy land!
There shall we find our place.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-weifeng-state-007__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
