      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·魏風·007.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">碩鼠.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>碩鼠碩鼠，無食我苗！三歲貫女，莫我肯勞。逝將去女，適彼樂郊。樂郊樂郊，誰之永號。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Large rats ! Large rats !
Do not eat our springing grain!
Three years have we had to do with you,
And you have not been willing to think of our toil.
We will leave you,
And go to those happy borders,
Happy borders! Happy borders!
Who will there make us always to groan ?</seg>
      </tuv>
